The following conditions shall apply to any deposit made with the Bank of Zambia under the provisions of paragraph (e) of subsection (1) of section three, that is to say:
(a) if any cash is deposited the Governor of the Bank may invest such cash in securities in the name of the building society making the deposit and such securities shall be deemed to be securities deposited by that society;
