(d) any references in this Act to total membership of a building society shall be construed as if the first named holder (but none of the other joint holders) is a member of the society;
any references in this Act to total membership of a building society shall be construed as if the first named holder (but none of the other joint holders) is a member of the society;
(e) the entry in the register of members to be kept under section twenty of the name and address of a person who is one of the joint holders (other than the first named holder) of shares shall indicate that he is a joint holder who is not the first named holder;
